      <title>南非财政部长要求非国大避免组建鲁莽联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-anc-will-ensure-policy-certainty-godongwana-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长埃诺克·戈东瓦纳表示，非洲人国民大会在失去议会多数席位后不会“鲁莽”选择联盟伙伴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-anc-will-ensure-policy-certainty-godongwana-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 07:01:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非大选后纷争让投资者陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非大选未能产生绝对胜利者，联盟谈判的结果仍存在很大不确定性，投资者准备迎接南非金融市场的进一步动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-african-election-coalition-talks-leave-investors-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
